          <td height="28" align="left" valign="top" class="headline"><h1>Dealers, Installers and Designers </h1></td>
          <td align="left" valign="top" class="headline"><img src="../graphics/landscapes/SanG3.jpg" width="196" height="50" border="1" align="right"></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td colspan="2" align="left" valign="top"><p>Forno Bravo works with a network of dealers, including retail hearth, fireplace, wood stove, BBQ, grill, outdoor kitchen and hot tub stores, masons, home builders and Italian plasterers. Our dealers provide consumers and restaurants with local expertise, installation services, oven demonstration, cooking classes, and great craftsmanship.</p>
            <p>Contact us directly if you have any questions, or if you do not find a Dealer near you. We are here to help.</p>
            <p>James Bairey<br>
              Forno Bravo, LLC<br>
              (707) 836-0105<br>
              james@fornobravo.com
            </p>
            <p>We are actively recruiting new dealers, so please get in touch with us if you are looking to expand your business.</p>
            <p class="textbold">CALIFORNIA</p>
            <p class="textbold">California Wine Country</p>
            <p>Fired Up Kitchens<br>
              1083 Vine St, #129<br>
            Healdsburg, CA 95448<br>
            peter@firedupkitchens.com<br>
            (707) 536-6794<br>
            Contact: Peter deJong</p>
            <p>Fired Up Kitchens specializes in outdoor kitchen and outdoor living space design, consulting and installation. Founded by Peter deJong, a successful restaurateur, restaurant designer, and classically trained chef featured on national television, Fired Up Kitchens installs Forno Bravo ovens in wood-fired kitchens and living spaces at wineries, homes and restaurants throughout the California wine country and beyond.</p>
            <p class="textbold">Central Valley</p>
            <p>Austin's Patio, Deck and Pool<br>
              701 I ST<br>
              Modesto, CA 95354 <br>
            (209) 524-1774<br>
            Contact: Bill Austin </p>
            <p>A high-end patio, pool and outdoor living store located in downtown Modesto, Austin's Patio, Deck and Pool is a local institution. Swing by an see the Forno Bravo Premio oven on display. </p>
            <p class="textbold">Sacramento and Foothills</p>
            <p class="textpage">Outdoor Kitchen Design<br>
              Contact: Jim Hemstalk<br>
              (916) 677-7337<br>
              jimhemstalk@ssctv.net</p>
            <p class="textpage">Professional design for the culinary enthusiast. Jim Hemstalk specializes in &quot;Tuscan Farm Kitchens&quot;  and heavy timber shade and/or covered structures. Jim's outdoor living spaces feature Forno Bravo pizza ovens and provide optimal functionality, and his group is very experienced with brick oven design and installation. Additional services include contractor selection, permit and engineering assistance, scheduling and project management.</p>
            <p class="textbold">Ventura</p>
            <p class="textpage">Fountain Depot, Inc. <br>
              11040 Nardo St.<br>
              Ventura, CA 93004<br>
              (805) 208-4876<br>
              Contact: Chris Thyfault<br>
              tefo@patiojunction.com </p>
            <p class="textpage">Check out Fountain Depot's large selection of outdoor design, cooking and living products, include Forno Bravo pizza ovens and fireplaces, along with ountains, pottery, statuary, firepits, and BBQ Islands. Visit Fountain Depot to see the Forno Bravo Casa pizza oven and Calore fireplace on display.</p>
            <p class="textbold">COLORADO</p>
            <p class="textbold">Boulder</p>
            <p>The Fire Within LLC<br>
            Box 1563<br>
            Boulder, Colorado<br>
            303.652.7378<br>
            Contact: Joseph Pergolizzi</p>
            <p>Joseph Pergolizzi is an Italian-American who has acquired many skills with stone dating back to his grandfather who was a mason in Italy. He has apprenticed with a German oven maker and Bio-dynamic gardener and has recently began working with Forno Bravo in creating wonderful indoor and outdoor kitchen spaces. We welcome any inquiry about residential or commercial sales and installations and to note custom made wood fired grills. Also a portable Forno Bravo oven is available to cater your next event. The menu includes pannini&rsquo;s, gourmet pizza, gelato and more. Consider planning a party before you decide on installing an oven so you can see why more Italians use Forno Bravo ovens than anything else. Grazie.</p>
            <p class="textbold">ILLINOIS</p>
            <p>Ken Shook Venetian Plastering and Italian Ovens <br>
              703 Third Street A <br>
              Moline IL 61265<br>
              GrRgChurch@aol.com <br>
              309-737-0935 <br>
            Cell: 309-797-4700 </p>
            <p>Ken Shook is an Italian-trained craftsman living in the Illinois Quad Cities USA, bringing authentic Italian and traditional American plaster wall treatments to residential and commercial customers everywhere. Ken utilizes his skills as an Italian Plasterer in the building of custom Argentine Grills and Wood-Fired Brick Ovens.</p>
            <p class="textbold">INDIANA</p>
            <p class="textbold"><img src="../graphics/Logos/RoseLogo.gif" width="80" height="50" border="1"></p>
