            <p>Rose Brick has been serving Indiana since 1914, when the company specialized in both building materials and heating fuel. Today, Rose Brick &amp; Materials not only has over 2.5 million brick in stock, but they also sell landscaping supplies, fireplaces, pizza ovens and tools.&nbsp; Rose Brick is a company that is both growing, and  maintaining superior quality and service. The company is now in its fifth generation, with Boyd's son Bobby coming aboard in May.</p>
